{
    "name": "滑索",
    "icon": "parcool:zipline_rope",
    "category": "parcool:category_support_features",
    "pages": [
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "滑索是一種跑酷設施，它能連接兩個遙遠的點，讓玩家能快速在兩地之間穿梭。"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:image",
            "border": "true",
            "images": [
                "parcool:textures/gui/entries/ride_zipline.png"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "title": "滑索掛鉤",
            "text": "首先決定滑索的兩個端點。接著我們需要在這兩個位置放置滑索掛鉤。$(br2)掛鉤共有兩種：木製掛鉤與鐵製掛鉤。"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "parcool:wooden_zipline_hook",
            "recipe2": "parcool:iron_zipline_hook"
        },
